            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日本股市在開市初段升逾1%，日經平均指數最低報33959，升374點或1.11%，最高見34325，升736點或2.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現升662點或1.97%，報34247點。</p>\n</div>",
